      "options": {
        "content": "## How to use this dashboard\n- Run the scripts in `scripts/verification/` to generate formal test evidence.\n- Raw artifacts are written under `test-results/` and the relative path is stored in the table above.\n- `Latest Logged Uptime`, `Response p50/p95`, `Ingest Success`, `Sustainable Concurrency`, and `Data Integrity Rate` come from completed verification runs, not from passive live scraping alone.\n- `Live API Availability (24h)` comes from Prometheus and is useful as a quick health cross-check.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
